# SamKirkland/FTP-Deploy-Action exclusion list
# Paths here are NEVER uploaded to the live server.
# One pattern per line; gitignore-style globs.

# Git metadata
.git
.gitignore
.github/

# Docs (theme internal — not needed on production)
README.md
DEPLOYMENT.md
*.md

# Dev tooling
node_modules/
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*.swo
*.tmp
*.bak

# Source files (the deployed CSS/JS is already minified-ready; keep originals out if you add a build step)
*.scss
*.map
